cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with language modeling using visual features, which suggests that it could belong to multiple sub-categories. The most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) since the paper deals with language modeling. The second most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) since the paper incorporates visual features. The third most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) since the paper deals with neural network models. The fourth most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) since the paper deals with multimodal models. The fifth most likely sub-category is cs.MM (Multimedia) since the paper deals with incorporating non-linguistic features.
